common Directory Reference

Files

file  hw_pmhal_bgap_common_data.c
 Band gap Temperature Sensor data common between tda2xx and tda3xx is defined in this file. The temperature to ADC conversion is also defined here.
 
file  hw_pmhal_common_ina226data.h
 This file contains the APIs to access the INA226 power measurement data structure.
 
file  hw_pmhal_common_vmdata.h
 This file contains the APIs to access the voltage domain structure.
 
file  hw_pmhal_data.h
 This file contains macros and data-structures pertaining to StarterWare PRCM (internal) implementation.
 
file  hw_pmhal_prmdata.h
 This file contains the APIs to access the PRM Interrupt device specific functions.
